in your life, Buddy!

32:21.330 --> 32:22.984
Susan, your dad--

32:23.028 --> 32:26.596
- I am not the one hiding in
a basement, attacking people!

32:26.640 --> 32:27.815
- I've only just begun.

32:27.858 --> 32:29.817
- Oh, yeah? What's next?
- I don't know.

32:29.860 --> 32:31.601
- What else are you gonna do
to win a high school election?

32:31.645 --> 32:33.429
- Whatever it takes!

32:38.565 --> 32:41.394
