I would, but...

36:19.046 --> 36:21.744
- You've got bigger fires
to put out.

36:21.788 --> 36:23.442
- I'll make sure
she gets home safe.

36:23.485 --> 36:25.705
- Thank you. Thank you.
Get home.

36:31.624 --> 36:33.278
- What were you thinking?

36:33.321 --> 36:34.975
