36:35.018 --> 36:37.456
- I'm just trying to help.
- I didn't ask for your help.

36:37.499 --> 36:39.632
- Yeah, I noticed.
- Richie.

36:39.675 --> 36:41.808
We thought
we were gonna die in there.

36:41.851 --> 36:44.941
- Yeah?
Did Buddy hold you real close?

36:44.985 --> 36:47.596
Because I saw you two
snuggling up earlier.

36:48.902 --> 36:51.818
- I--I know
how that must have looked.

36:51.861 --> 36:53.820
